    "feat": {
        "name": "Vellumis Excision",
        "type": "stat_block_section",
        "subtype": "feat",
        "text": "You seek to excise the rot from the Gravelands and have made progress to do so. You can cast *field of life* as a 6th-rank halcyon spell, and you gain a 6th-rank halcyon spell slot. When you cast your halcyon *field of life* as a primal spell, any living creatures in the area when you Sustain the spell gain a +2 status bonus to saving throws against curses, diseases, and poisons for 1 round.",
